    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-04-11T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-04-11T00:00:00-05:00" n="720"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d720">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72/9499</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Liberia</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_BRC1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bundy</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Monrovia</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-04-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 11, 1918</hi>
                        </date>. <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received April 12, 10.35
                        a.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>As yet threatened destruction of cable station by submarine has not been
                    attempted. Submarine not seen since about 7 last evening. Liberian Government
                    vessel, named <hi rend="italic">President <persName>Howard</persName>
                    </hi>, sunk yesterday by submarine. Result of running fight yesterday in view of
                    Monrovia between merchant steamer and submarine obscured by darkness. No
                    casualties among foreigners.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_BRC1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bundy</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
